<item>
            <title>[LU-14591] &quot;llite.*.dump_page_cache&quot; should not be included in &quot;lctl get_param -R &apos;*&apos;&quot; output</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14591</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &quot;&lt;tt&gt;llite.&amp;#42;.dump_page_cache&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; output should be excluded by default from &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl get_param -R &apos;&amp;#42;&apos;&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; output, since it can be &lt;b&gt;very&lt;/b&gt; verbose (millions of lines), and is almost always not useful unless looking for specific issues related to the page cache.  It should only be shown if explicitly requested by name.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
